{"tid":1995603,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"寵物界  超級金黃店告急！ 撐5.1黃金週","createTime":"2020-04-30T11:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T06:22:16.000Z","uid":275677,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"09a23b48f6f11a89a2ae0357bd04ab7e86ef7cef","tid":1995603,"uid":275677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2kpoeQ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2kpoeQ9.jpg&h=d93f6061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真人識佢，超級金黃小店<br />\n<br />\n佢搞寵物酒店。<br />\n<br />\n店主幫助好多流浪狗，自己仲要收留成十隻流浪狗。仲要有三罷，有入寵物界公會。<br />\n<br />\n逆情早期佢有賣寵物都用得既清潔用品，佢一直都冇加過價。<br />\n<br />\n知道佢最近因為冇人去旅行，已經冇咩人放狗仔去狗酒店。<br />\n<br />\n經營好有困難。大家有養貓狗既幫手懲罰佢。<br />\n<br />\nIg:sweety_pet_sitter<br />\n<br />\nFacebook:sweety_pet_sitter<br />\n<br />\n無養都幫手比個like share比朋友啦"},{"pid":"d1113ab085fd572447fcac3f8a39a929575795ff","tid":1995603,"uid":275677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手推post！黃店不可得一兩間，全人類推廣黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"2c8338e33c8f0660ae854394be6247018160d16e","tid":1995603,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"啲貓同狗望落住得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a33aacdf3ffdca8fd280464a2183ef5c2ab15df","tid":1995603,"uid":275677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8338e33c8f0660ae854394be6247018160d16e","tid":1995603,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"啲貓同狗望落住得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"咁就快d share啦，佢都有野賣架。"},{"pid":"859bdb1781156c1684d9809703589fbceac0c1b0","tid":1995603,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bddd7272966